### Unit Tests
1. Test error sets data to null in production mode
2. Test error uses mock data in development mode
3. Test usingMockData flag is set correctly
4. Test toast is called on error

### Integration Tests
1. Mock API failure, verify error UI shown
2. Verify mock data banner appears in dev mode
3. Verify no mock data in production build

### E2E Tests
1. Build production, fail API, verify error shown (not mock)
2. Dev mode, fail API, verify mock banner shown
3. Verify toast notifications appear

